{"tid":548674,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打睇過 歡迎加入nhk ?","createTime":"2018-02-02T20:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T08:27:40.000Z","uid":85084,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a211c131fabd236379581cce6ab22d2bd295611","tid":548674,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T20:32:16.000Z","msg":"見好似無乜人討論 搜尋keyword 又得1個post 仲要無人回 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟岩岩睇完 好有感觸 成個人好空虛<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔至於男主角感廢 但好多位都好有共嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班長阿哥 同佐藤講果段說話真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n山崎真係真男人 自己一個打工存錢 出城供自己讀書 <br />\n去到佢要番鄉下果集真係好灰, 成套戲即卡無唒笑位<br />\n<br />\n女主角人設普普通通 但故事加上聲優加乘 越睇越中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/042952_ce4c1d2aaed912300a78ccab0d60de7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F042952_ce4c1d2aaed912300a78ccab0d60de7b.png&h=6d0705c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然套野有d位都幾無里頭 但整體上我覺得都好睇 值得推介 ! <br />\n未睇過既巴打我建議可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後有個位唔係幾明,究竟 佐藤 同小岬有冇一齊到?"},{"pid":"e7ff4014d22e331eb987c1866eab7110029179a0","tid":548674,"uid":112760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T20:46:09.000Z","msg":"有，漫畫一齊咗"},{"pid":"8f7619baa23d93b3e75e1e5179bebde582c0a35c","tid":548674,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T23:32:53.000Z","msg":"首主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca1cd2dd367875303971d41b042eca693efe2a1","tid":548674,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T00:37:30.000Z","msg":"連登咁新 梗係得一個po<br />\n<br />\n漫畫後期亂咁黎<br />\n<br />\n動畫好d"},{"pid":"eb6504bd